  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel queues are long",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to fuel shortage, people were standing in long queues to get fuel in many areas including Colombo today (29).",
        "Due to non-availability of fuel stocks, many gas stations can be seen today as well, and many gas stations have displayed the sign that there is no diesel.",
        "The petrol station owners say that despite ordering the fuel stocks, they are not getting the proper stocks."
      ],
